HEADWORD: Ziment-water
<hw>Zim"ent-wa`ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[G.
<ets>cement-wasser</ets>. See <er>Cement</er>.]</ety> <def>A kind of
